00:10:14.274 --> 00:10:17.123
⟨un⟩ eyn tsayt in Katshergin zaynen zey, zaynen mir gevezn.

00:10:17.123 --> 00:10:18.710
ober ale yor tsu forn

00:10:18.710 --> 00:10:21.469
un nemen, nemen tsimern un zitsn oyf datshe

00:10:21.469 --> 00:10:23.111
iz gevezn dos tsu tayer.

00:10:23.792 --> 00:10:26.065
iz eyn yor fleg ikh zayn bay di tante

00:10:26.340 --> 00:10:30.435
UNK un UNK flegn mir ge- di mame aleyn gedungen a tsimer, ober nit ale yor.

00:10:30.187 --> 00:10:32.611
dertseylt undz bit vos iz KOLOTOVE, Katshergin.

00:10:32.448 --> 00:10:34.504
dos iz di, di ⟨forshtetn⟩ fun Kovne

00:10:34.504 --> 00:10:37.500
zeyer fayne forshtetn, mit a sakh ve- mit a sakh vald.

00:10:37.500 --> 00:10:41.319
mit UNK Nyemen iz gevezn. Der Nyemen iz geven a reyne, m'hot zikh kenen bodn.

00:10:41.477 --> 00:10:42.956
geven vayse zamd

00:10:43.687 --> 00:10:45.650
un zeyer a fayne vald.

00:10:45.695 --> 00:10:48.637
guter vald. KOLOTOV- iber hoypt in KOLOTOVO heyst dos lebn

00:10:48.637 --> 00:10:50.275
lebn, nit vayt

00:10:50.275 --> 00:10:52.181
s'iz geven a draysik kilometer fun Kovne

00:10:52.226 --> 00:10:53.680
zeyer a guter vald.

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:55.612
un dortn iz geven zeyer gut afile

00:10:56.057 --> 00:10:58.228
far kranke oykhet, mit lungen kranke.

00:10:58.301 --> 00:11:01.282
iz dort geven a sanatorye vu es flegn zayn a sakh mit lungen kranke.

00:11:05.490 --> 00:11:06.778
azoy arum az

00:11:06.806 --> 00:11:08.572
der lebn iz gegangen

00:11:08.628 --> 00:11:10.512
azoy shtil un ruik.

00:11:11.312 --> 00:11:13.669
un bay ayer tante iz geven a groyse mishpokhe?

00:11:13.775 --> 00:11:14.512
ya.

00:11:14.940 --> 00:11:19.198
mayn tante hot gehat dray tekhter; zey aleyn zaynen UNK gelebt in Kovne

00:11:19.198 --> 00:11:22.392
zey hobn gelebt oyf Vilner gas

00:11:22.685 --> 00:11:24.780
un zey hobn gehat a groysn gesheft

00:11:24.780 --> 00:11:26.173
fun papir.

00:11:28.085 --> 00:11:31.387
der onkl un, zey hobn UNK beyde gearbet in gesheft.

00:11:31.494 --> 00:11:35.893
un eyn tokhter zeyere iz geven in gesheft a bukhhalterin; zi hot gefirt di bukhhalterye in gesheft.

00:11:36.438 --> 00:11:38.970
un beyde yingere meydlekh hobn gelernt.

00:11:41.585 --> 00:11:46.130
⟨oykh⟩ azoy iz, in tsayt fun der milkhome hobn zey gelitn azoy vi ale hobn gelitn.

00:11:47.002 --> 00:11:49.528
oykh geven in geto, oykh gevezn in di lagern.

00:11:49.533 --> 00:11:52.020
un oyf, dertseylt a bisl vegn ayer dire.

00:11:52.031 --> 00:11:54.877
ir hot gelebt di gantse tsayt far der milkhome in eyn dire?

00:11:54.377 --> 00:11:58.337
neyn, mir hobn gelebt ⟨in⟩ ershtn, mir hobn ⟨zikh⟩ gelebt in altshtot

00:11:58.663 --> 00:12:00.590
un shpeter hobn mir zikh UNK

00:12:00.590 --> 00:12:01.897
azoy fil ikh gedenk

00:12:02.021 --> 00:12:03.619
in altshtot hobn mir gelebt

00:12:03.877 --> 00:12:07.466
in eyn ort altshot oyf eyn gas, dakht zikh oyf Birshtoner gas

00:12:07.607 --> 00:12:09.359
un ⟨eyn ort⟩ oyf Vilner gas

00:12:09.395 --> 00:12:13.456
un shpeter hobn mir gelebt di gantse tsayt oyf SAVANORIU PROSPEKTAS.

00:12:14.492 --> 00:12:19.110
 baym, bizn letstn, bizn letstn tog biz arayngeyn in geto mir gelebt SAVANORIU nayn un tsvantsik.

00:12:19.082 --> 00:12:22.485
un in dem zelbikn hoyz hot der foter gehat oykh zayn varshtat?

00:12:22.187 --> 00:12:24.375
neyn, neyn, dem foter hot gehat gedungen

00:12:24.515 --> 00:12:28.680
a kl- kl- kley- a kleynem, nu, a tsimer, nit keyn kleynem, a tsimer

00:12:28.683 --> 00:12:31.524
oykhet oyf itster heys- UNK hot geheysn LUKSIO

00:12:31.524 --> 00:12:32.644
LUKSIO gas

00:12:33.088 --> 00:12:35.074
un itster heyst dos SVENTOS GERTRUDOS

00:12:35.315 --> 00:12:36.102
gas.

00:12:36.446 --> 00:12:40.001
un dortn hot er gearbet, er mitn, mitn bruder un nokh a lern yingl.

00:12:40.698 --> 00:12:43.865
un ir gedenkt vi ayer bruder hot zikh gelernt oyf a zeyger makher?

00:12:44.765 --> 00:12:48.270
dos gedenk ikh ya. der pape flegt im avekzetsn afile un shtub

00:12:48.270 --> 00:12:51.943
iz geven a varshtat. tomer a mol flegt er im bavayzn dortn oyf der arbetn, flegn zey nemen

00:12:51.943 --> 00:12:54.429
iz geven aza min tish lebn, lebn fentster

00:12:54.772 --> 00:12:56.828
un er flegt

00:12:56.828 --> 00:12:57.719
arbetn.

00:12:58.670 --> 00:13:02.444
efsher gedenkt ir, vos far a fardinstn umgefer zaynen geven bay ayer foter?

00:13:02.703 --> 00:13:05.060
keyn groyse fardinstn iz nit gevezn.

00:13:05.235 --> 00:13:08.031
mir hobn zikh keyn shtark ⟨z- zikh⟩ nit gekent erloybn.

00:13:08.846 --> 00:13:13.295
ober optsuesn un tsu, tsum lebn aza min lebn mir zoln kenen lernen

00:13:13.554 --> 00:13:14.775
un

00:13:14.775 --> 00:13:17.464
zol nit feln keyn broyt, keyn, keyn

00:13:17.553 --> 00:13:18.543
fleysh.

00:13:18.633 --> 00:13:19.927
dos hot nit gefelt.

00:13:20.085 --> 00:13:24.510
ober zikh erloybn tsu forn in oysland oder vu, dos hobn mir zikh nit gekent erloybn.

00:13:24.388 --> 00:13:27.262
az di mame flegt geyn koyfn fleysh oder andere zakhn

00:13:27.262 --> 00:13:29.512
flegt ir ven nit iz bagleytn ayer muter?

00:13:30.767 --> 00:13:31.650
neyn.

00:13:31.897 --> 00:13:33.438
ikh fleg hobn

00:13:33.438 --> 00:13:35.497
mayne interesn; ikh fleg lernen.

00:13:35.497 --> 00:13:37.157
ikh fleg zingen in khor.

00:13:37.263 --> 00:13:39.164
ikh fleg holt hobn zeyer oysneyen.

00:13:40.132 --> 00:13:40.703
un

00:13:40.703 --> 00:13:43.682
gehat khavertes; shpeter flegn mir shabes geyn oyf tents.

00:13:43.727 --> 00:13:45.628
UNK vos geven mayne eygene interesn.

00:13:45.735 --> 00:13:48.784
dertseylt a bisl vegn ayer lerer, vegn ayer zingen in khor.

00:13:49.278 --> 00:13:52.647
bay undz in sh- in shul flegt zayn der, in shul geven a khor

00:13:53.143 --> 00:13:57.679
nu, un mir flegn zingen dortn un lernen UNK shpeter gevezn

00:13:57.679 --> 00:14:01.152
oys- oysneyen ⟨flegt men⟩ undz lernen; fleg ikh zeyer geyn oyf di

00:14:02.002 --> 00:14:04.376
dortn ⟨mitn, der⟩ lererin vos flegt undz lernen.

00:14:04.955 --> 00:14:06.243
a lererin iz dos gevezn.

00:14:06.243 --> 00:14:08.108
un shpeter iz flegn mir

00:14:08.145 --> 00:14:09.222
azoy geyn

00:14:09.222 --> 00:14:12.493
shpatsirn, batrakhtn vos tsum vos tsu neyen, vos tsu makhn.

00:14:12.954 --> 00:14:14.570
farshidene azelkhe interesn.

00:14:14.034 --> 00:14:16.897
vos iz geven di lern shprakh in ayer shul?

00:14:16.700 --> 00:14:19.951
litvish gevezn der, di, vayl s'iz geven a, a

00:14:20.328 --> 00:14:22.106
a melukhe gimnazye iz dos gevezn.

00:14:22.106 --> 00:14:26.195
un derfar iz geven, ikh hob gelernt in a melukhe gimnazye, vayl es iz geven veyniker tsum tsoln oykh.

00:14:26.943 --> 00:14:30.569
⟨azoy⟩ biliker, un shpeter hot men geklert efsher iz laykhter geven ontsukumen in

00:14:30.569 --> 00:14:31.624
hoykh shul

00:14:31.635 --> 00:14:32.425
in

00:14:32.425 --> 00:14:33.502
universitet.

00:14:34.082 --> 00:14:37.991
iz arum az zey hobn, zey hobn bashlosn, di eltern, bashlosn az beser zol ikh geyn in a

00:14:39.583 --> 00:14:40.640
in aza min shul.

00:14:40.612 --> 00:14:43.655
efsher gedenkt ir, vifl iz geven der, monatlekher

00:14:43.700 --> 00:14:46.226
oder der yoriker optsol in a litvishe gimnazye?

00:14:46.113 --> 00:14:47.604
bashtimt ken ikh nit visn

00:14:47.604 --> 00:14:50.903
gedenken, ober umgefer dakht zikh mir, iz dakht zikh mir azoy

00:14:50.903 --> 00:14:54.275
vi ikh gedenk az finf un zibetsik lit dakht zikh far a yor.

00:14:55.698 --> 00:14:58.834
un s'iz geven ⟨ober⟩ azoy oykhet, ver es iz geven zeyer oreme kinder

00:14:58.834 --> 00:15:00.058
flegn zey ongebn

00:15:00.069 --> 00:15:01.920
bites, un me flegt zey oplozn

00:15:02.195 --> 00:15:02.881
fun

00:15:03.427 --> 00:15:04.909
fun tsolungen.

00:15:04.946 --> 00:15:07.657
in, bay undz in litvishe shul iz gegangen

00:15:07.713 --> 00:15:09.716
in mayn klas iz gevezn

00:15:10.059 --> 00:15:11.538
finf yidishe meydlekh.

00:15:12.320 --> 00:15:14.650
un di iberike iz ale geven litviner.

00:15:14.480 --> 00:15:17.780
un in ayer klas iz geven nor meydlekh tsi meydlekh mit yinglekh tsuzamen?

00:15:16.870 --> 00:15:18.595
neyn, mir hobn gelernt bazunder.

00:15:18.595 --> 00:15:21.177
meydlekh bazunder un yinglekh bazunder. mir hobn gelernt

00:15:21.177 --> 00:15:25.089
ober in, beshas iz arayn di di, di, di rusn, di sovyetishe

00:15:25.297 --> 00:15:27.856
iz hobn tsu ⟨undz⟩ tsuzamenge-

00:15:28.588 --> 00:15:32.649
gebrakht, un mir hobn gelernt shoyn dem letstn yor hobn mir gelernt yinglekh mit meydlekh tsuzamen.

00:15:33.195 --> 00:15:34.940
un azoy geven bazundere shuln.

00:15:34.848 --> 00:15:37.408
ir hot shoyn bavizn endikn di, di mitl UNK

00:15:36.806 --> 00:15:38.676
ya, dem letsn tog

00:15:38.676 --> 00:15:41.002
grade dem letstn tog, dos iz gevezn

00:15:41.278 --> 00:15:43.382
dem tsvantsikstn yuni

00:15:44.619 --> 00:15:46.608
dem tsvantsikstn yuni

00:15:46.608 --> 00:15:49.862
hobn mir gele- ge- gehat dem letsn, geven shabes

00:15:50.913 --> 00:15:53.121
neyn, dos iz geven tsu fraytik; ikh gedenk bashtimt nit

00:15:53.121 --> 00:15:55.396
hobn mir gehat dem letstn ekzamen fun daytsh

00:15:56.668 --> 00:15:59.160
un ikh hob im oysgehaltn; dos iz geven der letster ekzamen

00:15:59.570 --> 00:16:00.830
un f-

00:16:01.106 --> 00:16:04.402
zuntik hot zikh ongehoybn, m'hot gehert az zikh ongehoybn di milkhome.

00:16:04.430 --> 00:16:05.810
un rikhtik nokh

00:16:05.810 --> 00:16:11.009
az far dem, dos gedenk ikh vi haynt, es iz geven fraytik tsi donershtik; ikh ken nit gedenken ven

00:16:11.009 --> 00:16:16.907
ober s'iz gef- zaynen geven geshtanen lebn shul, un shoyn getrakht vu mir veln geyn beshas es vet zayn der UNK bal

00:16:16.918 --> 00:16:18.313
vu veln mir geyn

00:16:18.369 --> 00:16:19.927
iz zaynen gefloygn

00:16:19.927 --> 00:16:21.519
eroplanen zaynen gefloygn.

00:16:22.706 --> 00:16:25.217
zogt nor di yinglekh, litviner zaynen gevezn

00:16:25.217 --> 00:16:26.129
"du zest?

00:16:26.129 --> 00:16:29.113
ot flien daytshene eroplanen."

00:16:29.692 --> 00:16:31.301
zogt "du vest nokh nit ervartn

00:16:31.301 --> 00:16:33.132
zoln kumen dokh daytshishe eroplanen."

00:16:33.132 --> 00:16:33.860
dos iz geven der

00:16:33.860 --> 00:16:35.812
punkt a por teg far milkhome.

00:16:36.054 --> 00:16:37.022
iz di daytshishe

00:16:37.022 --> 00:16:39.019
di litvishe yinglekh hobn gevart oyf di daytshn?

00:16:39.176 --> 00:16:42.076
nu. di etlekhe hobn shoyn gevart, vayzt oys az zey hobn gevust

00:16:42.076 --> 00:16:44.115
un zey hobn gezogt az daytshn veln kumen.

00:16:44.492 --> 00:16:46.902
n- zogt mir, ir hot zikh far der milkhome

00:16:46.905 --> 00:16:50.663
vu nit iz gelernt leyenen, shraybn yidish, a bisl hebreish?

00:16:51.140 --> 00:16:54.459
ikh hob zikh nit gelernt, ober fun shtub

00:16:55.072 --> 00:16:58.964
der pape un di mame geredt hobn mir oyf, in shtub oyf yidish

00:16:59.848 --> 00:17:05.287
un ikh hob sh- fun zikh, fun shtub, vayl ale hobn geredt, ale hobn ge⟨UNK⟩, un ikh hob zikh oysgelernt

00:17:05.287 --> 00:17:06.950
shraybn un leyenen yidish.

00:17:06.950 --> 00:17:08.595
fleg leyenen yidishe bikher

00:17:08.639 --> 00:17:11.978
kh'hob zeyer a, s'iz geven Spektor's bikher iz gevezn

00:17:11.978 --> 00:17:13.511
zeyer interesante.

00:17:16.777 --> 00:17:18.159
ver hot aykh gelernt?

00:17:18.159 --> 00:17:20.211
der, di muter tsi der foter

00:17:20.211 --> 00:17:24.890
alts eynts, y- alts eyns hot men ir gemuzt, lernen leyenen un shraybn.

00:17:24.754 --> 00:17:28.951
di muter hot mir gelernt, un der foter vos UNK der foter hot mir gelernt; beyde hobn zey mir gelernt.

00:17:29.058 --> 00:17:29.671
zey hobn

00:17:29.671 --> 00:17:32.883
der bruder hot mir gelernt hebreish. der bruder mayner iz geven a BETARist.

00:17:33.277 --> 00:17:34.970
z- dertseylt, vos iz a BETARist?

00:17:34.577 --> 00:17:36.727
dos iz a, an

00:17:36.727 --> 00:17:38.740
rekhte organizatsye, shtark rekht azoy

00:17:38.740 --> 00:17:40.848
andere flegn zogn s'iz a fashistishe organizatsye.

00:17:41.293 --> 00:17:44.443
un, merer, merer militerishe organizatsye iz dos gevezn.

00:17:44.988 --> 00:17:48.180
un beshas ⟨iz⟩ arayn di rusn hot er zeyer moyre gehat me zol im nit aroysfirn.

00:17:48.144 --> 00:17:50.433
ir gedenkt ayer bruder alts a BETARist?

00:17:50.270 --> 00:17:51.668
ikh gedenk im mit a broyne

00:17:51.668 --> 00:17:53.583
mit a broyne hemdl iz er gegangen

00:17:53.583 --> 00:17:57.234
un nokh mit a rimendl ib- ibergeleygt do.

00:17:57.560 --> 00:17:59.020
dos gedenk ikh zeyer gut.

00:18:00.412 --> 00:18:01.692
iz er flegt geyn

00:18:01.692 --> 00:18:02.730
dortn oyf di

00:18:03.045 --> 00:18:04.187
zamlungen.

00:18:04.563 --> 00:18:05.075
un

00:18:05.075 --> 00:18:06.730
vu hot zikh gelernt ayer bruder?

00:18:06.723 --> 00:18:09.935
fun onfang hot er zikh gelernt in, in real gimnazye.

00:18:09.963 --> 00:18:14.362
un shpeter hot er UNK zeks klasn dakht zikh hot er geendikt. ikh gedenk vayl er iz geven a sakh sh- elter fun mir

00:18:14.705 --> 00:18:17.225
un nokh dem hot er nit gevolt mer lernen.

00:18:17.225 --> 00:18:19.638
vayzt oys er hot gelernt tsu forn in, in Palestine

00:18:19.638 --> 00:18:20.842
tsi UNK

00:18:22.502 --> 00:18:25.570
UNK iz er hot ⟨gevelt⟩ dem zeyge- dem zeyger

00:18:25.570 --> 00:18:28.048
dos lernen, der foter UNK, ober der foter hot im

00:18:28.222 --> 00:18:30.194
ahingeredt, un shpeter

00:18:30.194 --> 00:18:32.877
iz er geven zeyer tsufridn, vayle der fakh

00:18:32.880 --> 00:18:36.851
hot er gekent di zey- di, di, makhn di zeygers, farrikhtn heyst dos.

00:18:36.851 --> 00:18:40.249
hot im geholfn in lager, in daytshn lager in DACHAU.

00:18:40.305 --> 00:18:42.977
un der- derfar hot der foter mitn bruder

00:18:42.977 --> 00:18:46.140
geblibn lebn, vayle zey hobn gearbet bay zayn fakh.

00:18:46.177 --> 00:18:50.266
di daytshn flegn zey avekzetsn in a budke un gebn zeyere zeygers farrikhtn

00:18:50.266 --> 00:18:52.010
un zey hobn dan nit gedarft arbetn ⟨shver⟩.

00:18:52.010 --> 00:18:55.632
fun di onfang hobn zey zeyer shver gearbet, un zey voltn azoy gearbet, voltn zey nit gekent

00:18:55.632 --> 00:18:56.561
oyslebn.

00:18:56.589 --> 00:18:58.480
zey voltn nit geblibn lebn fun DACHAU.

00:18:58.327 --> 00:19:01.848
tsvishn aykh un ayere, ayer bruder iz a groyser untersheyd fun yorn?

00:19:00.760 --> 00:19:03.010
n- a groyser, ya, akht yor.

00:19:03.010 --> 00:19:04.847
m'hot, mistamen iz dos derfar

00:19:04.847 --> 00:19:10.078
vayle der foter iz gevezn, genumen in armey, fertsntn y- in fertsntn yor hot men im genumen in armey

00:19:10.078 --> 00:19:13.526
un gek- un der bruder mayner iz gevezn dan zeks monat

00:19:13.650 --> 00:19:16.176
tsi zeks tsi finf monat, umgefer azoy fil.

00:19:16.822 --> 00:19:20.945
un fun ⟨armey der⟩ foter iz gekumen mistamen in tsvantsiktsn yor, UNK azoy.

00:19:20.945 --> 00:19:22.099
umgefer azoy.

00:19:22.357 --> 00:19:24.000
tsvantsik tsi nayntsn tsi eyn un tsvantsik.

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:24.916
dos ken ikh bashtimt nit zign.

00:19:25.293 --> 00:19:28.826
ver fun di mishpokhe mitglider, ayer tate mame

00:19:28.826 --> 00:19:32.325
oder dem bruder ho- der bruder hot gehat oyf aykh dem grestn virkung?

00:19:33.444 --> 00:19:36.980
der pape hot mir zeyer holt gehat, un der pape hot ⟨gehat oyf mir dem grestn⟩ virkung.

00:19:37.292 --> 00:19:39.601
UNK ale mol dertseyln vegn di milkhome

00:19:39.601 --> 00:19:41.701
az di daytshn zaynen geven zeyer shlekhte

00:19:41.701 --> 00:19:43.597
beshas er iz geven in gefangenshaft

00:19:43.788 --> 00:19:46.567
zey flegn, di daytshn flegn for oyf ferdn

00:19:47.467 --> 00:19:49.240
un zey flegn UNK

00:19:49.240 --> 00:19:52.283
di, di farhaftlinge flegt men fir- firn in kolones

00:19:52.283 --> 00:19:55.697
un zey flegn zey mit- fun oybn, fun di ferdn, flegn zey zey hargenen.

00:19:56.310 --> 00:19:59.440
dos flegt der pape dertseyln, UNK dos gedenk ikh nokh biz haynt.

00:20:00.731 --> 00:20:02.463
ikh hob mit im zeyer fil mitlayd.

00:20:03.347 --> 00:20:04.250
mitn foter.

00:20:03.735 --> 00:20:05.214
fun foter, ya, zeyer.

00:20:07.520 --> 00:20:08.622
itster

00:20:08.915 --> 00:20:12.183
UNK mir veln UNK itster nemt on dertseyln vi s'iz

00:20:12.585 --> 00:20:16.125
vos iz geven, ye, fun di ershte, ershter tog fun der milkhome.

00:20:12.735 --> 00:20:13.680
di milkhome.

00:20:16.745 --> 00:20:21.500
zikh ongehoybn di milkhome, UNK der pape hot gehert radyo zogt az zikh ongehoybn di milkhome.

00:20:21.500 --> 00:20:23.110
di daytshn, az di daytshn

00:20:23.110 --> 00:20:26.510
vos di daytshn tuen op mit yidn hobn mir shoyn lang gevust

00:20:26.651 --> 00:20:29.400
vayle s'iz geven in Kovne zeyer a sakh gelof-

00:20:29.400 --> 00:20:30.935
gekumen tsu loyfn fun Poyln

00:20:30.935 --> 00:20:32.164
un fun Daytshland.

00:20:33.553 --> 00:20:34.982
un zey hobn dertseylt

00:20:36.135 --> 00:20:37.946
az vos es tut zikh opet

00:20:37.946 --> 00:20:41.042
az me darf loyfn. derfar zaynen zey gelofn fun Daytsh- fun Daytshland.

00:20:41.042 --> 00:20:43.244
gevezn etlekhe vos zey flegn kumen tsum foter

00:20:43.244 --> 00:20:45.344
afile eyner iz geven a fabrikant vos er flegt hobn

00:20:45.364 --> 00:20:49.474
mit zey UNK brengen di zeygers, teyln fun zeygers un tsuzamenshteln zeygers.

00:20:49.474 --> 00:20:50.186
⟨nor dan⟩

00:20:51.035 --> 00:20:53.741
un, un fun Poyln gevezn.

00:20:53.741 --> 00:20:57.300
iz er bakant mit yidishe yinglekh vos zaynen gekumen fun Poyln, un zey hobn dertseylt.

00:20:57.988 --> 00:21:00.159
hobn mir ale bashlosn az me darf

00:21:00.992 --> 00:21:02.775
loyfn fun danet in Rusland.

00:21:02.730 --> 00:21:04.204
antshuldikt, ir hot aleyn geredt

00:21:04.204 --> 00:21:05.106
gehert vi di

00:21:05.106 --> 00:21:06.234
plitim dertseyln?

00:21:06.155 --> 00:21:08.770
ya, ikh hob aleyn gehert, vayl ikh hob zikh gekhavert

00:21:08.770 --> 00:21:11.654
mit eynem, az eyner ah fun Poyln, a yidisher yingl iz gevezn.

00:21:11.654 --> 00:21:14.413
flegt er kumen tsu undz un dertseyln. shpeter iz geven eyner a yid

00:21:14.413 --> 00:21:16.663
a yingl fun Daytshland, GUNTHER

00:21:16.922 --> 00:21:18.547
iz er geven shpeter in geto.

00:21:18.558 --> 00:21:22.631
hot er oykh dertseylt az er mit di tante gelofn, di eltern hobn zikh farlorn mit di eltern

00:21:22.631 --> 00:21:23.970
un er hot dertseylt

00:21:24.093 --> 00:21:25.404
az s'iz shreklekh

00:21:25.882 --> 00:21:29.505
un me mu- me, oyb me ken darf men fun d-, fun dan antloyfn.

00:21:30.050 --> 00:21:32.106
un ayer foter, ayer mishpokhe

00:21:32.126 --> 00:21:34.916
ven s'iz do gekumen di bolshevikes in fertsikstn yor

00:21:34.916 --> 00:21:36.671
ven Rusland hot farkhapt Lite

00:21:34.991 --> 00:21:35.381
ya

00:21:36.601 --> 00:21:37.220
ya

00:21:36.699 --> 00:21:38.837
zey hobn nisht gehat keyn tsores fun dem makht?

00:21:39.433 --> 00:21:43.174
m'hot zey, UNK keyn tsores nit gehat. der pape iz keyn mol nit geven keyn parteyener

00:21:43.652 --> 00:21:45.536
un nit di mame, nit der pape.

00:21:45.677 --> 00:21:51.662
un, un der bruder hot gets- gehat shreklekh zeyer fil moyre, vayle me zol im arestirn aroysfirn in Rusland

00:21:52.376 --> 00:21:57.703
un der pape iz, hot men i- in ARTEL, alemen in ARTEL tsugenumen.

00:21:58.181 --> 00:22:03.325
m'hot im ⟨farshlosn⟩ zayn MAISTERSKAYA zayn eygene, un arayngeyn in ARTEL. UNK in ARTEL UNK shpeter dertseyln

00:22:03.325 --> 00:22:05.954
az in ARTEL hot er gearbet mit a sakh dortn litviner oykh.

00:22:08.323 --> 00:22:11.979
un beshas, ⟨zayt⟩ shoyn biz zikh ongehoybn di milkhome

00:22:12.508 --> 00:22:14.471
hobn mir bashlosn tsu fun Kovne

00:22:14.471 --> 00:22:15.054
tsu

00:22:15.054 --> 00:22:15.686
loyfn.

00:22:15.731 --> 00:22:18.678
mir hobn gevelt forn mitn ban. mir zaynen gelofn tsu

00:22:18.785 --> 00:22:20.349
mh ban shtot

00:22:21.080 --> 00:22:24.213
un men hot undz gezogt az der letster eshalon iz shoyn avek.

00:22:24.455 --> 00:22:27.217
ir gedenkt dos vifl a zeyger tsi dem ershtn tog iz dos geven?

00:22:27.493 --> 00:22:30.525
neyn, dos iz shoyn gevezn nit der ershter tog.

00:22:31.037 --> 00:22:34.131
dem ershtn tog hobn mir nor gevart vos ven, vu ven, vos

00:22:34.131 --> 00:22:36.161
dos iz gevezn montik in der fri.

00:22:36.386 --> 00:22:38.304
montik UNK baginen zaynen mir gelofn.

00:22:38.478 --> 00:22:43.890
nor vayzt oys UNK nit rikhtik. s'iz avek nor eyn eshalon, un az mir zaynen gekumen hot men gezogt az der tsveyter eshalon iz shoyn avek

00:22:43.890 --> 00:22:44.900
⟨vider⟩ avek eshalon.

00:22:44.900 --> 00:22:46.380
dan UNK nit rikhtik

00:22:46.380 --> 00:22:47.298
informirt.

00:22:48.215 --> 00:22:51.647
azoy hobn mir bashlosn az mir mitn eshalon kenen mir shoyn nit forn

00:22:51.658 --> 00:22:53.222
darfn mir geyn tsu fus.

00:22:53.345 --> 00:22:56.208
un azoy vi mir hobn gelebt oyf SAVANORIU PROSPEKTAS

00:22:56.535 --> 00:22:58.926
dortn iz ⟨vayt⟩ hobn mir genumen di veg oyf Yaneve.

00:22:59.690 --> 00:23:03.346
hobn mir genumen dos vos me ken mit zikh, iber hoypt esnvarg hobn mir UNK genumen

00:23:03.420 --> 00:23:04.866
un mir zaynen gelozn in veg.

00:23:05.225 --> 00:23:06.598
s'iz gevezn heys.

00:23:06.598 --> 00:23:07.633
s'iz geven zumer.

00:23:08.398 --> 00:23:10.293
ful mentshn zaynen gelofn.

00:23:10.338 --> 00:23:12.206
iz di gasn zaynen geven ful.

00:23:13.798 --> 00:23:16.121
sakh zaynen, a sakh hobn zikh opgetsoygn.

00:23:16.177 --> 00:23:17.994
az mir zaynen aroys oyfn shosey

00:23:18.202 --> 00:23:22.685
shoyn hinter k- hinter, dos, SAVANORIU PROSPEKTAS ⟨dortn⟩ iz gevezn

00:23:23.248 --> 00:23:25.532
iz mesershmitn zaynen geforn

00:23:25.532 --> 00:23:28.271
un zikh zeyer aru- arunterlozn zeyer niderik

00:23:28.361 --> 00:23:30.009
un genumen shisn.

00:23:30.437 --> 00:23:33.005
un zey hobn alemen ba- ba- azoy hobn bashosn.

00:23:33.005 --> 00:23:35.465
a sakh mentshn hot men getrofn, gefaln.

00:23:35.465 --> 00:23:39.766
eyne iz ⟨gelegn⟩ a froy un dem kind ⟨vos zi⟩ hot bahaltn UNK hinter zikh; der kind iz geblibn; di froy iz geven

00:23:39.766 --> 00:23:40.944
shoyn a

00:23:41.051 --> 00:23:42.227
geshtorbene.

00:23:42.823 --> 00:23:49.669
mit eyn vort, a sakh dortn farlorn eltern mit, mit kinder, muters mit kinder hot geshreyen; di veyneray iz gevezn shreklekh.

00:23:50.079 --> 00:23:52.875
bay tog flegn mir geyn; bay nakht flegn mir zikh ruen.

00:23:53.252 --> 00:23:54.917
nit vayt fun Yaneve

00:23:55.310 --> 00:23:56.910
hot men undz gezogt

00:23:57.167 --> 00:24:00.941
az Yaneve iz shoyn farnumen; in Yaneve iz shoyn do a daytsher desant

00:24:02.162 --> 00:24:03.810
un

00:24:04.035 --> 00:24:05.430
Yaneve brent.

00:24:06.127 --> 00:24:07.623
der brik iz shoyn nito.

00:24:07.680 --> 00:24:09.396
me ken shoyn dortn nit geyn.

00:24:09.789 --> 00:24:11.120
mit eyn vort

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:12.871
bashlosn me darf geyn shoyn tsurik.

00:24:15.240 --> 00:24:16.972
UNK oysgematerte

00:24:17.028 --> 00:24:20.752
kh'hob shoyn, shoyn ge- gehat di esn vos shoyn kimat nit gehat.

00:24:20.859 --> 00:24:21.984
hungerike.

00:24:22.563 --> 00:24:24.701
in veg zaynen mir gevezn kimat a vokh.

00:24:24.977 --> 00:24:28.076
⟨geven⟩ dray teg mistamen oyf Yaneve, un mistamen dray teg tsurik.

00:24:29.246 --> 00:24:30.590
geyendik tsurik

00:24:30.748 --> 00:24:34.387
farshmutsikte, farshtoybte, nit gevashn a gantse vokh

00:24:34.511 --> 00:24:36.176
iz gevezn grade zuntik.

00:24:36.232 --> 00:24:38.741
di zun hot geshaynt; geven zeyer a sheyner tog.

00:24:39.118 --> 00:24:41.250
un mir, un mir ale fir

00:24:41.295 --> 00:24:43.807
grade zaynen mir ale fir gekumen

00:24:43.826 --> 00:24:45.160
in shtub gliklekh.

00:24:45.632 --> 00:24:47.814
mayn tante mitn onkl

00:24:47.814 --> 00:24:51.181
zey hobn zikh farlorn, beshas iz geven di- beshas m'hot bombardirt.

00:24:51.181 --> 00:24:55.440
der onkl mit di, mit di kuzine, mayne kuzine iz oykhet punkt in mayne yorn gevezn.

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:57.220
oykhet ⟨iz zi⟩ geven a nayntsn yor.

00:24:57.782 --> 00:24:59.095
zi mitn foter hobn zikh

00:24:59.098 --> 00:25:03.690
f- in eyn zayt gevezn, un di muter mit, mit di tsvey t- beyde tekhter hobn zikh farlorn in a tsveyte zayt.

00:25:03.690 --> 00:25:06.610
beshas di t- kuzine mitn foter zaynen gegangen durkh a ander veg

00:25:06.610 --> 00:25:07.985
hot men zey farhaftet.

00:25:08.328 --> 00:25:09.521
vayzt oys

00:25:09.662 --> 00:25:10.669
di

00:25:11.602 --> 00:25:13.554
mit vayse, mit di vayse

00:25:13.424 --> 00:25:14.514
bender

00:25:13.627 --> 00:25:14.735
zey, bender, ya

00:25:14.842 --> 00:25:16.900
m'hot zey avekgefirt oyfn fort.

00:25:16.900 --> 00:25:20.442
oyfn, mistamen oyfn tsveytn fort tsi oyfn UNK fort veys ikh nit; kh'ken nit zogn

00:25:20.442 --> 00:25:23.274
un ikh veys az dem fort, dem onkl hot men dortn geshosn

00:25:23.938 --> 00:25:26.854
un shtelt zikh for, vi nit, vi nit

00:25:26.854 --> 00:25:27.867
dos iz

00:25:27.887 --> 00:25:29.791
az di, di kuzine mayne

00:25:29.810 --> 00:25:33.406
mir zitsn in shtub beshas ⟨m'iz⟩ gekumen gliklekh arayn in shtot

00:25:33.406 --> 00:25:35.306
gliklekh in sht- keyner hot ⟨mir⟩ nit farhaftet.

00:25:35.306 --> 00:25:39.350
mir zaynen arayn in shtub; alts hobn mir gefunen in di zelbe UNK mir hobn gelozn. keyner hot undz nit barabevet.

00:25:39.378 --> 00:25:41.021
keyner hot keyn zakh nit geganvet.

00:25:41.032 --> 00:25:42.511
grade hobn mir alts gefunen.

00:25:42.872 --> 00:25:45.735
un m'iz arayn in shtub; mir zaynen geven etlekhe teg azoy in shtub.

00:25:45.892 --> 00:25:48.637
me klapt in tir; es geyt arayn a daytsh.

00:25:48.980 --> 00:25:50.476
un m'hot mayn kuzine

00:25:51.579 --> 00:25:53.430
erfirt in shtub.

00:25:54.347 --> 00:25:55.728
zi hot im gebetn

00:25:55.730 --> 00:25:58.790
un vayzt oys zeyer a guter, a mentshlekher mentsh.

00:25:58.802 --> 00:25:59.736
dos iz gevezn

00:25:59.736 --> 00:26:02.756
an, aza min nes az ikh, ikh ken, ikh ken nit dertseyln.

00:26:02.756 --> 00:26:05.664
un ikh gedenk nokh vi haynt az der foter hot im gegebn a zeygerl

00:26:06.159 --> 00:26:08.764
un er hot ir avekgefirt; zey hobn gelebt oyf NEMUNO gas

00:26:08.764 --> 00:26:11.008
un er hot ir avekgefirt in shtub

00:26:11.008 --> 00:26:11.772
bay zikh

00:26:14.512 --> 00:26:17.561
zikh gezesn, gezesn, aroysgeyn hot men nit getort.

00:26:17.904 --> 00:26:20.500
vayle az me flegt aroysgeyn in gas, flegt men

00:26:20.500 --> 00:26:22.421
glaykh farhaftn

00:26:23.861 --> 00:26:25.976
un beshas ⟨mir zaynen⟩ azoy gezesn in shtub

00:26:25.976 --> 00:26:27.056
eyn mol

00:26:27.056 --> 00:26:28.782
kumt arayn eyner

00:26:30.071 --> 00:26:33.238
a litviner vos er hot gearbet tsuzamen mitn pape

00:26:33.682 --> 00:26:35.313
oykh a zeyger makher

00:26:35.657 --> 00:26:36.750
a hoy-

00:26:36.939 --> 00:26:40.595
un er zogt dem fa- dem foter mit, mitn, mit, mitn bruder

00:26:40.736 --> 00:26:41.625
"kumt

00:26:42.170 --> 00:26:43.391
kumt in Gestapo"

00:26:43.391 --> 00:26:44.241
mitn biks

00:26:44.988 --> 00:26:47.000
der fo- ya, neyn, ya

00:26:46.271 --> 00:26:47.483
er hot gehat a vaysn band?

00:26:47.020 --> 00:26:48.577
a vaysn band, ya.

00:26:48.080 --> 00:26:50.800
dertseylt a bisl vegn di mentshn vegn, mit di vayse be-

00:26:49.376 --> 00:26:54.382
ikh nit gede- ikh ke- ikh ken im nit, dakht zikh ken im nit, ikh ken nit zogn az ikh veys bashtimt, a hoykher

00:26:54.438 --> 00:26:57.228
un er hot genumen der foter mitn, mitn bruder

00:26:57.228 --> 00:26:58.747
un avekgefirt in

00:26:58.747 --> 00:27:00.047
Gestapo do oyf

00:27:00.047 --> 00:27:01.892
VYTAUTO PROSPEKTAS.

00:27:02.488 --> 00:27:04.280
er hot arayngefirt UNK

00:27:04.428 --> 00:27:07.353
hobn mir shoyn mir di mame gezogt shoyn, nokh alemen

00:27:07.353 --> 00:27:08.895
"mir blaybn shoyn beyde aleyn."

00:27:10.368 --> 00:27:11.496
beshas

00:27:11.499 --> 00:27:14.760
mir zitsn azoy, mir ⟨va-⟩. mir ⟨hobn⟩ shoyn gor oyf zey nit gehoft.

00:27:14.760 --> 00:27:16.010
in gantsn nit gehoft.

00:27:17.523 --> 00:27:19.593
mit a mol mir zeen

00:27:19.650 --> 00:27:21.298
beyde kumen zey.

00:27:22.248 --> 00:27:23.629
zey geyen arayn in shtub.

00:27:23.666 --> 00:27:25.020
hobn zey dertseylt

00:27:25.472 --> 00:27:28.386
az beshas m'hot zey arayngefirt in

00:27:28.678 --> 00:27:29.921
Gestapo

00:27:31.327 --> 00:27:33.059
gezesn dort a daytsh

00:27:33.234 --> 00:27:38.173
tsi a feld UNK tsi vos UNK veys nit ver dortn mit im, oder hoykhe, mit a hoykhe rang

00:27:38.668 --> 00:27:40.100
un er hot gezogt

00:27:40.237 --> 00:27:41.750
"vos hot ir azoy dort gebrakht?

00:27:42.178 --> 00:27:46.796
a ordenung muz zayn a ordenung. fir zey tsurik; me vet makhn a geto; dan vet men zey firn in geto."

00:27:48.624 --> 00:27:51.760
un er hot zey gemuzt avek, un er hot zey avekgefirt tsurik in shtub.

00:27:51.760 --> 00:27:52.940
zaynen zey gekumen in shtub.

00:27:54.024 --> 00:27:56.560
ts- tsu vos far a tsvek hot er zey gefirt in Gestapo?

00:27:56.749 --> 00:27:59.219
er hot gevelt me zol arestirn ayer foter?

00:27:56.820 --> 00:28:00.954
mista- me z- me zol, me zol arestirn dem foter me- mitn bruder.

00:28:00.926 --> 00:28:04.262
ir hot, er hot zey zalbe tsvey UNK zey dem foter, zay dem bruder?

00:28:03.542 --> 00:28:05.376
say dem foter, say dem bruder.

00:28:06.798 --> 00:28:08.871
nu, shoyn azoy zaynen zey gekumen gliklekh.

00:28:08.871 --> 00:28:11.790
iz nit lang zaynen mir gevezn in, in sh- bay zikh in

00:28:11.790 --> 00:28:12.270
shtub

00:28:12.270 --> 00:28:14.997
nu, UNK undzer shokhnte dortn iz gevezn

00:28:14.997 --> 00:28:17.339
an, a eltere froy iz zi gevezn

00:28:17.649 --> 00:28:22.903
flegt zi undz al- aleyn flegn mir hobn moyre aroystsugeyn in gas, flegt zi brengen, mir flegn ir gebn gelt vayle gelt hobn mir nokh gehat

00:28:22.903 --> 00:28:26.084
flegn mir gebn gelt, fleg zi undz brengen broyt, flegt zi brengen shpayz

00:28:26.084 --> 00:28:29.220
un azoy iz mir UNK biz vanet UNK gevezn UNK arayngefirt in geto.

00:28:29.276 --> 00:28:31.440
un di shokhnte ayere, zi iz nisht geven keyn yidishe?

00:28:31.318 --> 00:28:32.747
neyn, neyn, a litvishe.

00:28:33.123 --> 00:28:36.150
a litvishe. a, a yidishe flegt nit kenen, me flegt hobn moyre tsu geyn

00:28:36.150 --> 00:28:39.061
nu mentshn flegn geyn, me flegt rizikirn, me flegt arunternemen di lates

00:28:39.061 --> 00:28:42.951
ober di mame flegt mir nit lozn geyn. eyn mol iz zi aleyn aroysgegangen

00:28:42.951 --> 00:28:45.800
un mir mitn bruder flegt zi beshum oyfn nit lozn geyn; zi flegt

00:28:45.800 --> 00:28:48.250
⟨vartn⟩ UNK. aleyn flegt zi geyn.

00:28:47.163 --> 00:28:49.329
un in ayer shtub vu s- vu ir zayt

00:28:49.329 --> 00:28:50.229
vu ir hot gelebt

00:28:50.319 --> 00:28:53.480
hobn gelebt a sakh yidishe un nisht keyn yidishe mishpokhes?

00:28:53.390 --> 00:28:55.530
es hobn gelebt a mishpokhe

00:28:55.530 --> 00:28:59.628
oykh a gekumene fun Daytshland, zaynen zey gekumen in a yor fertsikstn yor

00:29:01.946 --> 00:29:04.829
in fertsikstn yor, un beshas mir zaynen gelofn

00:29:04.829 --> 00:29:06.845
oyf, oyf Yaneve fun, fun di rusn

00:29:06.845 --> 00:29:07.863
hobn mir gezogt

00:29:07.920 --> 00:29:09.613
farges-, fargesn zeyer familye.

00:29:09.613 --> 00:29:14.039
mit tsvey, a froy mit a man mit a kind, hobn zey gezogt "neyn, mir loyfn nit; mir UNK beser do blaybn."

00:29:14.079 --> 00:29:15.029
a yidishe mishpokhe.

00:29:14.822 --> 00:29:16.010
a yidishe mishpokhe.

00:29:15.949 --> 00:29:17.530
ir hot zikh ⟨nokh dem⟩ getrofn mit zey?

00:29:16.914 --> 00:29:17.527
neyn.

00:29:17.527 --> 00:29:20.639
zaynen, vayzt oys zaynen zey, mir, az mir zaynen gekumen tsurik in shtub zaynen zey shoyn nit gevezn.
